videos.headline: Gueldner cashes 3 for Drake
videos.description: Sarah Beth Gueldner knocks down the 3-pointer from the top of the key for an early Drake lead.

videos.headline: Weidner caps 12-0 run for Nebraska with sweet layup
videos.description: Allison Weidner pulls Nebraska level as she puts in the scoop layup in the lane.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Weidner caps 12-0 run for Nebraska with sweet layup) 2022/11/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Dinnebier's layup forces a Nebraska timeout
videos.description: Drake goes up 15 early in the second half as Katie Dinnebier scorees the layup, forcing a Nebraska timeout.
